cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about object localization using deep learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The datasets used in the experiments are medical images, which fall under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a new framework for weakly supervised learning, which could also be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
